{
  "texts": [
    "• This study introduces a unique framework that integrates deep learning and recommender systems for forecasting student enrolment and improving retention strategies.",
    "• The optimal features are selected using the Pythagorean fuzzy AHP with hybrid optimization technique.",
    "The proposed hybrid optimization approach-IEPO, is developed by combining TLBO, EMA, and EPO.",
    "This approach significantly improves feature selection, resulting in better model accuracy and efficiency.",
    "• The research work introduces the DeepEnrollNet model, including CNN, GRU, and Attention QCNN in prediction."
  ]
}